{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775888086377,"sessionID":"ses_284d26f6cffep1c53tLhzWJxzP","part":{"id":"prt_d7b2db2f0001BxQ10REeW1w2VN","messageID":"msg_d7b2da200001Nxt0efn4osNAXa","sessionID":"ses_284d26f6cffep1c53tLhzWJxzP","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-23e0f9acc1874d0a95a484ce7c2ce8e5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/CHANGE.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/CHANGE.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-033 — Makefile 构建目标体系\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: - **AR**: AR-033\n5: - **Title**: Makefile 构建目标体系\n6: - **Module**: root\n7: - **Language**: Makefile\n8: - **Size**: M\n9: - **Status**: Completed\n10: \n11: ## Description\n12: \n13: Makefile 构建目标体系，用于统一管理项目的构建、测试、清理等操作。\n14: \n15: ## Dependencies\n16: \n17: - Go toolchain 1.25+\n18: - Python 3.10+\n19: - Docker 20.10+ (for container builds)\n20: - GNU Make 4.0+\n21: \n22: ## Related Changes\n23: \n24: None\n25: \n26: ## Implementation Notes\n27: \n28: ### Files Created\n29: \n30: #### Core Files\n31: - **Makefile** - Root Makefile with all main targets and variables\n32: - **VERSION** - Version file for tracking project version (0.1.0)\n33: - **.gitignore** - Updated gitignore to exclude build artifacts\n34: \n35: #### Sub-Makefiles (.makefiles/)\n36: - **go.mk** - Go-specific build, test, and dependency management targets\n37: - **python.mk** - Python-specific build, test, and dependency management targets\n38: - **docker.mk** - Docker image build and management targets\n39: - **test.mk** - Test execution and coverage reporting targets\n40: - **lint.mk** - Code quality, formatting, and linting targets\n41: - **clean.mk** - Build artifact cleanup targets\n42: - **deps.mk** - Dependency management targets\n43: - **release.mk** - Release creation and packaging targets\n44: - **utils.mk** - Utility targets (info, check, CI, dev)\n45: - **docs.mk** - Documentation generation targets\n46: \n47: #### Build Scripts (scripts/)\n48: - **build.sh** - Build script for all components\n49: - **test.sh** - Test execution script\n50: - **release.sh** - Release creation script\n51: \n52: #### Directories Created\n53: - **bin/** - Build artifacts directory (in .gitignore)\n54: - **dist/** - Distribution packages directory (in .gitignore)\n55: - **coverage/** - Test coverage reports directory (in .gitignore)\n56: - **reports/** - Test reports directory (in .gitignore)\n57: - **.makefiles/** - Sub-Makefiles directory\n58: - **scripts/** - Build scripts directory\n59: \n60: ### Build Targets Summary\n61: \n62: #### Build Targets\n63: - `build` - Build all Go and Python components\n64: - `build-go` - Build all Go binaries\n65: - `build-python` - Build Python packages (wheel and sdist)\n66: - `build-agentd` - Build agentd binary\n67: - `build-picod` - Build picod binary\n68: - `build-agentcube` - Build agentcube CLI binary\n69: - `build-agentcube-util` - Build agentcube-util binary\n70: - `build-code-interpreter` - Build code-interpreter binary\n71: - `build-agent-runtime` - Build agent-runtime binary\n72: \n73: #### Test Targets\n74: - `test` - Run all tests (Go and Python)\n75: - `test-go` - Run all Go tests\n76: - `test-python` - Run all Python tests\n77: - `test-go-cover` - Generate Go test coverage report\n78: - `test-python-cover` - Generate Python test coverage report\n79: - `test-integration` - Run all integration tests\n80: - `test-e2e` - Run end-to-end tests\n81: \n82: #### Lint Targets\n83: - `lint` - Run all linting checks\n84: - `lint-go` - Run Go linting (gofmt, go vet, golangci-lint)\n85: - `lint-python` - Run Python linting (ruff, mypy, flake8)\n86: - `format` - Format all code\n87: - `format-go` - Format Go code (gofmt, goimports)\n88: - `format-python` - Format Python code (black, isort)\n89: \n90: #### Docker Targets\n91: - `docker-build` - Build all Docker images\n92: - `docker-build-agentd` - Build agentd Docker image\n93: - `docker-build-picod` - Build picod Docker image\n94: - `docker-build-agentcube` - Build agentcube Docker image\n95: - `docker-push` - Push all Docker images to registry\n96: \n97: #### Clean Targets\n98: - `clean` - Clean all build artifacts\n99: - `clean-go` - Clean Go build artifacts\n100: - `clean-python` - Clean Python build artifacts\n101: - `clean-all` - Clean all artifacts including reports\n102: \n103: #### Dependency Targets\n104: - `deps` - Download all dependencies\n105: - `deps-go` - Download Go dependencies\n106: - `deps-python` - Download Python dependencies\n107: - `deps-update` - Update all dependencies\n108: \n109: #### Release Targets\n110: - `release` - Create release build\n111: - `release-all` - Complete release process\n112: - `tag` - Create git tag for current version\n113: - `snapshot` - Create snapshot build\n114: \n115: #### Development Targets\n116: - `dev-setup` - Set up development environment\n117: - `dev-up` - Start development services\n118: - `dev-down` - Stop development services\n119: \n120: #### CI/CD Targets\n121: - `ci` - Run CI pipeline\n122: - `ci-build` - CI: Build all components\n123: - `ci-test` - CI: Run all tests\n124: - `ci-lint` - CI: Run all linting checks\n125: \n126: #### Utility Targets\n127: - `help` - Show help message\n128: - `version` - Display version information\n129: - `vars` - Display all Makefile variables\n130: - `info` - Display build information\n131: - `check-tools` - Check if required tools are installed\n132: \n133: ### Usage Examples\n134: \n135: ```bash\n136: # Show help\n137: make help\n138: \n139: # Build everything\n140: make build\n141: \n142: # Run all tests\n143: make test\n144: \n145: # Run linting\n146: make lint\n147: \n148: # Format code\n149: make format\n150: \n151: # Clean build artifacts\n152: make clean\n153: \n154: # Build in release mode\n155: BUILD_MODE=release make build\n156: \n157: # Create release\n158: make release-all\n159: ```\n160: \n161: ### Key Features\n162: \n163: 1. **Unified Interface** - Single entry point for all build operations\n164: 2. **Multi-language Support** - Go and Python build targets\n165: 3. **Cross-platform Builds** - Support for linux/amd64, linux/arm64, darwin/amd64, darwin/arm64\n166: 4. **Color-coded Output** - Improved readability with color-coded messages\n167: 5. **Comprehensive Help** - Self-documenting with `make help`\n168: 6. **CI/CD Friendly** - Targets designed for automated pipelines\n169: 7. **Development Mode** - Race detection and debug symbols by default\n170: 8. **Release Mode** - Optimized builds with stripped binaries\n171: 9. **Test Coverage** - Coverage reports for both Go and Python\n172: 10. **Docker Integration** - Build and push Docker images\n173: \n174: ### Test Coverage\n175: \n176: All Makefile targets have been designed and tested to ensure:\n177: - Targets execute successfully\n178: - Error messages are clear and helpful\n179: - Dependencies are properly managed\n180: - Build artifacts are placed in correct locations\n181: \n182: ## Deferred Items\n183: \n184: None\n\n(End of file - total 184 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-033 — Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-033\n- **Title**: Makefile 构建目标体系\n- **Module**: root\n- **Language**: Makefile\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Completed\n\n## Description\n\nMakefile 构建目标体系，用于统一管理项目的构建、测试、清理等操作。\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Go toolchain 1.25+\n- Python 3.10+\n- Docker 20.10+ (for container builds)\n- GNU Make 4.0+","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775888086344,"end":1775888086375}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775888086381,"sessionID":"ses_284d26f6cffep1c53tLhzWJxzP","part":{"id":"prt_d7b2db53a001EhEGYUuIvLdTQ5","messageID":"msg_d7b2da200001Nxt0efn4osNAXa","sessionID":"ses_284d26f6cffep1c53tLhzWJxzP","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-7ead3dbb9292466ca342ed85d1afe98f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube 项目在根目录创建统一的 Makefile 构建目标体系，提供标准化的构建、测试、清理、代码质量检查和容器镜像构建操作。该 Makefile 将整合 Go 二进制文件构建、Python 包管理、多语言测试、Docker 镜像构建以及开发工作流自动化，为开发者提供单一入口点来执行所有常见任务。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 实现统一的 Makefile 构建目标体系，达到以下目标：\n10: \n11: - **统一构建接口** - 提供单一入口点执行所有构建、测试、清理操作\n12: - **多语言支持** - 同时支持 Go 和 Python 项目的构建和测试\n13: - **开发效率提升** - 通过标准化的目标和别名简化常见操作\n14: - **CI/CD 友好** - 目标命名和输出格式便于 CI/CD 管道集成\n15: - **可扩展性** - 模块化设计便于添加新的构建目标和规则\n16: - **一致性** - 确保所有团队成员使用相同的构建命令和参数\n17: - **自文档化** - 通过 help 目标提供完整的使用说明\n18: \n19: ## Module\n20: \n21: `root` - 项目根目录\n22: \n23: ## Language\n24: \n25: Makefile (GNU Make 4.0+)\n26: \n27: ## Size\n28: \n29: M\n30: \n31: ## Scope\n32: \n33: ### In Scope\n34: \n35: 1. **Go 构建目标**\n36:    - `build` - 构建所有 Go 二进制文件（agentd、picod、router、workload-manager）\n37:    - `build-go` - Go 专用构建目标\n38:    - `build-agentd` - 构建 agentd 二进制文件\n39:    - `build-picod` - 构建 picod 二进制文件\n40:    - `build-router` - 构建 router 二进制文件\n41:    - `build-workloadmanager` - 构建 workload-manager 二进制文件\n42:    - `build-cli` - 构建 CLI 工具\n43: \n44: 2. **Python 构建目标**\n45:    - `build-python` - 构建 Python 包（wheel/sdist）\n46:    - `install-python` - 安装 Python 依赖\n47:    - `install-dev` - 安装开发依赖\n48: \n49: 3. **测试目标**\n50:    - `test` - 运行所有测试（Go + Python）\n51:    - `test-go` - 运行 Go 单元测试\n52:    - `test-python` - 运行 Python 单元测试\n53:    - `test-integration` - 运行集成测试\n54:    - `test-coverage` - 生成测试覆盖率报告\n55:    - `test-race` - 运行 Go 竞态检测测试\n56: \n57: 4. **代码质量目标**\n58:    - `lint` - 运行所有 lint 检查（Go + Python）\n59:    - `lint-go` - 运行 Go lint（golangci-lint）\n60:    - `lint-python` - 运行 Python lint（ruff）\n61:    - `format` - 格式化所有代码（Go + Python）\n62:    - `format-go` - 格式化 Go 代码（goimports）\n63:    - `format-python` - 格式化 Python 代码（black）\n64:    - `check` - 运行所有检查（lint + test）\n65: \n66: 5. **清理目标**\n67:    - `clean` - 清理构建产物\n68:    - `clean-go` - 清理 Go 构建产物\n69:    - `clean-python` - 清理 Python 构建产物\n70:    - `clean-docker` - 清理 Docker 镜像和容器\n71:    - `clean-all` - 清理所有产物和缓存\n72: \n73: 6. **Docker 构建目标**\n74:    - `docker-build` - 构建 Docker 镜像（多阶段）\n75:    - `docker-build-builder` - 构建开发镜像\n76:    - `docker-build-runtime` - 构建生产镜像\n77:    - `docker-push` - 推送镜像到仓库\n78:    - `docker-tag` - 为镜像打标签\n79: \n80: 7. **开发工具目标**\n81:    - `dev` - 启动开发环境\n82:    - `dev-up` - 启动所有开发服务（使用 Docker Compose）\n83:    - `dev-down` - 停止所有开发服务\n84:    - `dev-logs` - 查看开发服务日志\n85:    - `watch` - 监视文件变化并自动重新构建\n86:    - `run` - 运行本地开发服务器\n87: \n88: 8. **文档目标**\n89:    - `docs` - 生成项目文档\n90:    - `docs-serve` - 启动文档服务器\n91:    - `docs-build` - 构建文档静态站点\n92: \n93: 9. **依赖管理目标**\n94:    - `deps` - 下载所有依赖（Go + Python）\n95:    - `deps-go` - 下载 Go 依赖（go mod download）\n96:    - `deps-python` - 下载 Python 依赖（pip install）\n97:    - `deps-update` - 更新所有依赖\n98:    - `deps-verify` - 验证依赖完整性\n99: \n100: 10. **版本和发布目标**\n101:     - `version` - 显示版本信息\n102:     - `release` - 创建发布版本\n103:     - `tag` - 为当前代码打 Git 标签\n104: \n105: 11. **帮助和元目标**\n106:     - `help` - 显示所有可用目标和用法\n107:     - `list` - 列出所有目标\n108:     - `info` - 显示项目构建信息\n109:     - `vars` - 显示所有 Makefile 变量\n110: \n111: ### Out of Scope\n112: \n113: - CI/CD 管道配置（在单独的 AR 中处理）\n114: - Kubernetes 部署配置（已在其他 AR 中处理）\n115: - 监控和日志收集（在单独的 AR 中处理）\n116: - 性能测试和基准测试（在单独的 AR 中处理）\n117: - 跨平台构建工具（如 Bazel、Gradle）集成\n118: \n119: ## Impact Analysis\n120: \n121: ### Components Impacted\n122: \n123: 1. **项目根目录**\n124:    - 新增 `Makefile` 文件\n125:    - 新增 `.makefiles/` 目录用于包含子 Makefile\n126:    - 新增 `scripts/` 目录用于构建脚本\n127:    - 新增 `.dockerignore` 优化 Docker 构建\n128: \n129: 2. **Go 二进制文件构建**\n130:    - 所有 `cmd/*/` 目录下的 Go 应用需要支持通过 Makefile 构建\n131:    - 构建产物统一输出到 `bin/` 目录\n132:    - 支持交叉编译（amd64, arm64）\n133: \n134: 3. **Python 包管理**\n135:    - Python CLI 工具需要支持通过 Makefile 构建\n136:    - 依赖管理通过 Makefile 统一\n137:    - 支持虚拟环境创建和激活\n138: \n139: 4. **Docker 镜像构建**\n140:    - 整合 AR-032 的多阶段 Dockerfile 构建\n141:    - 统一镜像标签和命名规范\n142:    - 支持多架构镜像构建\n143: \n144: 5. **开发工作流**\n145:    - 开发者使用 `make help` 了解所有可用命令\n146:    - 标准化的构建和测试流程\n147:    - 简化的本地开发环境设置\n148: \n149: ### Dependencies\n150: \n151: | 依赖 | 版本要求 | 用途 |\n152: |------|---------|------|\n153: | GNU Make | 4.0+ | Make 执行引擎 |\n154: | Go | 1.24+ | Go 语言工具链 |\n155: | Python | 3.11+ | Python 运行时 |\n156: | Docker | 20.10+ | 容器镜像构建 |\n157: | golangci-lint | 1.50+ | Go lint 工具 |\n158: | ruff | 0.1+ | Python lint 工具 |\n159: | black | 23.0+ | Python 代码格式化 |\n160: | goimports | latest | Go import 格式化 |\n161: | pytest | 7.0+ | Python 测试框架 |\n162: | hadolint | 2.10+ | Dockerfile lint |\n163: \n164: ### Breaking Changes\n165: \n166: 无破坏性变更。这是一个新增功能，不影响现有构建流程。\n167: \n168: ### Performance Impact\n169: \n170: 1. **构建时间**\n171:    - 首次构建时间与现有流程相同\n172:    - 增量构建利用 Make 的依赖跟踪，可能更快\n173:    - 并行构建支持（`make -j`）\n174: \n175: 2. **磁盘空间**\n176:    - 增加约 10KB 的 Makefile 文件\n177:    - 构建产物与现有相同，无额外开销\n178: \n179: 3. **开发体验**\n180:    - 命令输入从复杂脚本简化为 `make target`\n181:    - Tab 补全支持（通过 bash/zsh 集成）\n182:    - 一致的错误消息和帮助输出\n183: \n184: ## Design Decisions\n185: \n186: ### Makefile 结构\n187: \n188: **选择**: 单一主 Makefile + 模块化子 Makefile\n189: \n190: **理由**:\n191: - 主 Makefile 提供统一入口\n192: - 子 Makefile 按语言/功能分离（`go.mk`, `python.mk`, `docker.mk`）\n193: - 便于维护和扩展\n194: - 支持选择性加载\n195: \n196: **目录结构**:\n197: ```\n198: / (root)\n199: ├── Makefile              # 主 Makefile\n200: ├── .makefiles/           # 子 Makefile 目录\n201: │   ├── go.mk            # Go 特定规则\n202: │   ├── python.mk        # Python 特定规则\n203: │   ├── docker.mk        # Docker 特定规则\n204: │   ├── test.mk          # 测试特定规则\n205: │   └── lint.mk          # Lint 特定规则\n206: ├── scripts/             # 构建脚本\n207: │   ├── build.sh\n208: │   ├── test.sh\n209: │   └── release.sh\n210: └── bin/                 # 构建产物输出目录\n211: ```\n212: \n213: ### 目标命名规范\n214: \n215: **选择**: 使用连字符分隔的小写单词（kebab-case）\n216: \n217: **理由**:\n218: - 与现有项目命名风格一致\n219: - 易于输入和记忆\n220: - 支持 Tab 补全\n221: - 与常见开源项目（Kubernetes, Docker）保持一致\n222: \n223: **示例**:\n224: - ✅ `build-agentd`, `test-python`, `clean-all`\n225: - ❌ `build_agentd`, `testPython`, `CLEAN_ALL`\n226: \n227: ### 变量命名规范\n228: \n229: **选择**: 大写下划线命名（UPPER_SNAKE_CASE）\n230: \n231: **理由**:\n232: - Makefile 标准约定\n233: - 与环境变量区分\n234: - 易于识别配置项\n235: \n236: **示例**:\n237: - `GO_VERSION`, `BUILD_DIR`, `DOCKER_REGISTRY`\n238: \n239: ### 构建产物目录\n240: \n241: **选择**: 统一输出到 `bin/` 目录\n242: \n243: **理由**:\n244: - 清晰的产物位置\n245: - 易于忽略（添加到 `.gitignore`）\n246: - 支持多平台构建（`bin/linux_amd64/`, `bin/linux_arm64/`）\n247: \n248: **目录结构**:\n249: ```\n250: bin/\n251: ├── agentd\n252: ├── picod\n253: ├── router\n254: ├── workload-manager\n255: ├── cli\n256: ├── linux_amd64/\n257: │   ├── agentd\n258: │   └── picod\n259: └── linux_arm64/\n260:     ├── agentd\n261:     └── picod\n262: ```\n263: \n264: ### 依赖管理策略\n265: \n266: **选择**: Makefile 负责依赖下载和验证\n267: \n268: **理由**:\n269: - 自包含的构建系统\n270: - 不依赖外部包管理器（如 dep、glide）\n271: - 与 Go modules 和 pip 集成良好\n272: \n273: **实现**:\n274: ```makefile\n275: deps: deps-go deps-python\n276: \n277: deps-go:\n278: \tgo mod download\n279: \tgo mod verify\n280: \n281: deps-python:\n282: \tpip install -r requirements.txt\n283: ```\n284: \n285: ### 并行构建支持\n286: \n287: **选择**: 使用 `.NOTPARALLEL` 控制并行性\n288: \n289: **理由**:\n290: - 某些目标需要串行执行（如 clean）\n291: - 其他目标可以并行（如 test-go, test-python）\n292: - 使用 `make -j` 启用并行构建\n293: \n294: **实现**:\n295: ```makefile\n296: # 默认允许并行\n297: .PHONY: test\n298: test: test-go test-python\n299: \n300: # 串行执行\n301: .PHONY: clean\n302: clean: .NOTPARALLEL\n303: clean: clean-go clean-python clean-docker\n304: ```\n305: \n306: ### Help 目标实现\n307: \n308: **选择**: 使用 awk 解析目标注释\n309: \n310: **理由**:\n311: - 自文档化，无需手动维护帮助文本\n312: - 与目标定义同步\n313: - 支持颜色和格式化输出\n314: \n315: **实现**:\n316: ```makefile\n317: help: ## Show this help message\n318: \t@echo \"$(BLUE)Available targets:$(NC)\"\n319: \t@awk 'BEGIN {FS = \":.*?## \"} /^[a-zA-Z_-]+:.*?## / {printf \"  $(YELLOW)%-20s$(NC) %s\\n\", $$1, $$2}' $(MAKEFILE_LIST)\n320: ```\n321: \n322: ### 虚拟目标（.PHONY）\n323: \n324: **选择**: 显式声明所有虚拟目标\n325: \n326: **理由**:\n327: - 避免与同名文件冲突\n328: - 提高构建性能（Make 不会检查文件时间戳）\n329: - 明确表示目标不生成文件\n330: \n331: **实现**:\n332: ```makefile\n333: .PHONY: build build-go build-python test clean lint help\n334: ```\n335: \n336: ### 条件编译支持\n337: \n338: **选择**: 使用 Make 条件语句和变量\n339: \n340: **理由**:\n341: - 支持不同构建场景（dev, prod, test）\n342: - 支持平台特定配置\n343: - 便于 CI/CD 集成\n344: \n345: **实现**:\n346: ```makefile\n347: ifeq ($(BUILD_MODE),release)\n348: \tBUILD_FLAGS := -ldflags=\"-s -w\"\n349: else\n350: \tBUILD_FLAGS := -race\n351: endif\n352: ```\n353: \n354: ### 环境变量支持\n355: \n356: **选择**: 支持通过环境变量覆盖配置\n357: \n358: **理由**:\n359: - CI/CD 友好\n360: - 支持不同环境配置\n361: - 灵活的构建选项\n362: \n363: **示例**:\n364: ```bash\n365: # 使用环境变量\n366: GO_VERSION=1.23 BUILD_MODE=release make build\n367: \n368: # 使用 make 变量\n369: make build GO_VERSION=1.23 BUILD_MODE=release\n370: ```\n371: \n372: ## Alternatives Considered\n373: \n374: ### Alternative 1: 使用多个独立 Makefile\n375: \n376: **描述**: 每个子模块（Go、Python、Docker）使用独立的 Makefile\n377: \n378: **优点**:\n379: - 模块化程度高\n380: - 各模块独立维护\n381: \n382: **缺点**:\n383: - 没有统一入口\n384: - 开发者需要记住多个 Makefile 位置\n385: - 无法实现跨模块目标（如 `make test`）\n386: \n387: **选择**: 不采纳 - 统一 Makefile 提供更好的用户体验\n388: \n389: ### Alternative 2: 使用 Shell 脚本替代 Makefile\n390: \n391: **描述**: 使用 shell 脚本（如 `build.sh`, `test.sh`）管理构建\n392: \n393: **优点**:\n394: - 简单直接\n395: - 易于调试\n396: - 跨平台\n397: \n398: **缺点**:\n399: - 缺少依赖跟踪\n400: - 无法增量构建\n401: - 不支持并行构建\n402: - 难以管理复杂的目标依赖\n403: \n404: **选择**: 不采纳 - Makefile 在构建管理方面更强大\n405: \n406: ### Alternative 3: 使用任务运行器（Task, Just）\n407: \n408: **描述**: 使用现代任务运行器替代 Make\n409: \n410: **优点**:\n411: - 更友好的语法\n412: - 内置跨平台支持\n413: - 丰富的功能\n414: \n415: **缺点**:\n416: - 需要额外安装\n417: - 不是标准工具\n418: - 学习曲线\n419: - 与现有工具生态不完全兼容\n420: \n421: **选择**: 不采纳 - Make 是 Unix 标准工具，更通用\n422: \n423: ### Alternative 4: 使用构建系统（Bazel, Gradle）\n424: \n425: **描述**: 使用高级构建系统管理整个项目\n426: \n427: **优点**:\n428: - 强大的依赖管理\n429: - 增量构建和缓存\n430: - 支持多语言\n431: \n432: **缺点**:\n433: - 复杂度高\n434: - 学习曲线陡峭\n435: - 对中小型项目过度设计\n436: - 需要大量配置\n437: \n438: **选择**: 不采纳 - 对 AgentCube 项目来说过于复杂\n439: \n440: ### Alternative 5: 完全分散的构建命令\n441: \n442: **描述**: 不提供统一构建接口，开发者直接调用语言特定工具\n443: \n444: **优点**:\n445: - 零配置\n446: - 完全灵活\n447: \n448: **缺点**:\n449: - 一致性差\n450: - 学习成本高\n451: - 容易出错\n452: - 不利于 CI/CD\n453: \n454: **选择**: 不采纳 - 需要统一接口提高开发效率\n455: \n456: ## Implementation Plan\n457: \n458: ### Phase 1: 基础结构 (Day 1)\n459: \n460: 1. 创建 `Makefile` 基础框架\n461: 2. 创建 `.makefiles/` 目录\n462: 3. 创建 `scripts/` 目录\n463: 4. 定义基础变量和常量\n464: 5. 实现 `help` 目标\n465: \n466: **检查清单**:\n467: - [ ] 根 Makefile 创建\n468: - [ ] `.makefiles/` 目录创建\n469: - [ ] `scripts/` 目录创建\n470: - [ ] 基础变量定义（GO_VERSION, BUILD_DIR 等）\n471: - [ ] `help` 目标实现\n472: - [ ] 颜色输出支持\n473: \n474: ### Phase 2: Go 构建目标 (Day 1-2)\n475: \n476: 1. 创建 `.makefiles/go.mk`\n477: 2. 实现 Go 构建规则\n478: 3. 实现 Go 测试规则\n479: 4. 实现 Go lint 规则\n480: 5. 实现依赖管理规则\n481: \n482: **关键目标**:\n483: - `build-go` - 构建所有 Go 二进制文件\n484: - `test-go` - 运行 Go 测试\n485: - `lint-go` - 运行 golangci-lint\n486: - `deps-go` - 下载 Go 依赖\n487: \n488: **检查清单**:\n489: - [ ] `.makefiles/go.mk` 创建\n490: - [ ] Go 构建规则\n491: - [ ] Go 测试规则\n492: - [ ] Go lint 规则\n493: - [ ] Go 依赖管理\n494: - [ ] 交叉编译支持\n495: \n496: ### Phase 3: Python 构建目标 (Day 2)\n497: \n498: 1. 创建 `.makefiles/python.mk`\n499: 2. 实现 Python 构建规则\n500: 3. 实现 Python 测试规则\n501: 4. 实现 Python lint 规则\n502: 5. 实现依赖管理规则\n503: \n504: **关键目标**:\n505: - `build-python` - 构建 Python 包\n506: - `test-python` - 运行 Python 测试\n507: - `lint-python` - 运行 ruff\n508: - `deps-python` - 安装 Python 依赖\n509: \n510: **检查清单**:\n511: - [ ] `.makefiles/python.mk` 创建\n512: - [ ] Python 构建规则\n513: - [ ] Python 测试规则\n514: - [ ] Python lint 规则\n515: - [ ] Python 依赖管理\n516: - [ ] 虚拟环境支持\n517: \n518: ### Phase 4: Docker 构建目标 (Day 2-3)\n519: \n520: 1. 创建 `.makefiles/docker.mk`\n521: 2. 整合 AR-032 的多阶段 Dockerfile\n522: 3. 实现 Docker 构建规则\n523: 4. 实现多架构构建支持\n524: 5. 实现镜像推送规则\n525: \n526: **关键目标**:\n527: - `docker-build` - 构建 Docker 镜像\n528: - `docker-build-multiarch` - 构建多架构镜像\n529: - `docker-push` - 推送镜像\n530: - `clean-docker` - 清理 Docker 资源\n531: \n532: **检查清单**:\n533: - [ ] `.makefiles/docker.mk` 创建\n534: - [ ] Docker 构建规则\n535: - [ ] 多架构支持\n536: - [ ] 镜像推送规则\n537: - [ ] 与 AR-032 集成\n538: \n539: ### Phase 5: 测试和 Lint 目标 (Day 3)\n540: \n541: 1. 创建 `.makefiles/test.mk`\n542: 2. 创建 `.makefiles/lint.mk`\n543: 3. 实现统一测试目标\n544: 4. 实现统一 lint 目标\n545: 5. 实现代码格式化目标\n546: \n547: **关键目标**:\n548: - `test` - 运行所有测试\n549: - `test-integration` - 运行集成测试\n550: - `test-coverage` - 生成覆盖率报告\n551: - `lint` - 运行所有 lint 检查\n552: - `format` - 格式化所有代码\n553: \n554: **检查清单**:\n555: - [ ] `.makefiles/test.mk` 创建\n556: - [ ] `.makefiles/lint.mk` 创建\n557: - [ ] 统一测试目标\n558: - [ ] 统一 lint 目标\n559: - [ ] 代码格式化目标\n560: - [ ] 覆盖率报告生成\n561: \n562: ### Phase 6: 清理和维护目标 (Day 3)\n563: \n564: 1. 实现清理目标\n565: 2. 实现信息显示目标\n566: 3. 实现依赖更新目标\n567: 4. 实现版本管理目标\n568: \n569: **关键目标**:\n570: - `clean` - 清理构建产物\n571: - `clean-all` - 清理所有产物和缓存\n572: - `info` - 显示构建信息\n573: - `deps-update` - 更新依赖\n574: \n575: **检查清单**:\n576: - [ ] 清理目标实现\n577: - [ ] 信息显示目标\n578: - [ ] 依赖更新目标\n579: - [ ] 版本管理目标\n580: - [ ] `vars` 目标（显示所有变量）\n581: \n582: ### Phase 7: 开发工具目标 (Day 4)\n583: \n584: 1. 实现开发环境目标\n585: 2. 实现监视和重载目标\n586: 3. 实现本地运行目标\n587: 4. 创建 Docker Compose 配置（如果需要）\n588: \n589: **关键目标**:\n590: - `dev` - 启动开发环境\n591: - `dev-up` - 启动所有服务\n592: - `watch` - 监视文件变化\n593: - `run` - 运行本地服务器\n594: \n595: **检查清单**:\n596: - [ ] 开发环境目标\n597: - [ ] 服务启动/停止目标\n598: - [ ] 文件监视目标\n599: - [ ] Docker Compose 配置（如需要）\n600: \n601: ### Phase 8: 文档目标 (Day 4)\n602: \n603: 1. 创建 `.makefiles/docs.mk`\n604: 2. 实现文档生成目标\n605: 3. 实现文档服务器目标\n606: 4. 集成 Docusaurus（项目使用）\n607: \n608: **关键目标**:\n609: - `docs` - 生成文档\n610: - `docs-serve` - 启动文档服务器\n611: - `docs-build` - 构建文档站点\n612: \n613: **检查清单**:\n614: - [ ] `.makefiles/docs.mk` 创建\n615: - [ ] 文档生成规则\n616: - [ ] 文档服务器规则\n617: - [ ] Docusaurus 集成\n618: \n619: ### Phase 9: 集成和测试 (Day 5)\n620: \n621: 1. 集成所有子 Makefile\n622: 2. 测试所有目标\n623: 3. 验证并行构建\n624: 4. 验证跨平台构建\n625: 5. 性能基准测试\n626: \n627: **检查清单**:\n628: - [ ] 主 Makefile 集成\n629: - [ ] 所有目标测试\n630: - [ ] 并行构建测试\n631: - [ ] 跨平台构建测试\n632: - [ ] 性能基准\n633: - [ ] 错误处理测试\n634: \n635: ### Phase 10: 文档和优化 (Day 5-6)\n636: \n637: 1. 编写 Makefile 注释\n638: 2. 创建使用文档\n639: 3. 创建最佳实践指南\n640: 4. 优化构建性能\n641: 5. 添加 Tab 补全支持\n642: \n643: **检查清单**:\n644: - [ ] Makefile 注释\n645: - [ ] 使用文档\n646: - [ ] 最佳实践指南\n647: - [ ] 性能优化\n648: - [ ] Tab 补全脚本\n649: - [ ] README 更新\n650: \n651: ## Testing Strategy\n652: \n653: ### Unit Tests\n654: \n655: 1. **Makefile 语法测试**\n656:    - 验证 Makefile 语法正确性\n657:    - 测试变量展开\n658:    - 测试条件语句\n659: \n660: 2. **目标可用性测试**\n661:    - 验证所有目标可以执行\n662:    - 测试目标依赖关系\n663:    - 验证 `.PHONY` 声明\n664: \n665: ### Integration Tests\n666: \n667: 1. **端到端构建测试**\n668:    - 从干净状态运行 `make build`\n669:    - 验证所有产物正确生成\n670:    - 验证产物位置和命名\n671: \n672: 2. **测试执行测试**\n673:    - 运行 `make test`\n674:    - 验证所有测试通过\n675:    - 验证测试报告生成\n676: \n677: 3. **Docker 构建测试**\n678:    - 运行 `make docker-build`\n679:    - 验证镜像成功构建\n680:    - 测试镜像可以运行\n681: \n682: 4. **并行构建测试**\n683:    - 运行 `make -j build`\n684:    - 验证并行执行正确\n685:    - 验证无竞态条件\n686: \n687: ### Cross-Platform Tests\n688: \n689: 1. **Linux amd64**\n690:    - 验证 Go 交叉编译\n691:    - 验证 Docker 镜像构建\n692:    - 验证测试执行\n693: \n694: 2. **Linux arm64**\n695:    - 验证 Go 交叉编译\n696:    - 验证 Docker 镜像构建\n697:    - 验证测试执行（如果硬件可用）\n698: \n699: 3. **macOS**\n700:    - 验证 Make 兼容性\n701:    - 验证路径处理\n702:    - 验证依赖安装\n703: \n704: ### Performance Tests\n705: \n706: 1. **构建时间基准**\n707:    - 测量 `make build` 时间\n708:    - 测量增量构建时间\n709:    - 对比并行 vs 串行构建\n710: \n711: 2. **缓存效率测试**\n712:    - 验证源代码未变时使用缓存\n713:    - 验证依赖未变时使用缓存\n714: \n715: 3. **磁盘空间测试**\n716:    - 测量构建产物大小\n717:    - 验证 `make clean` 清理彻底\n718: \n719: ### Regression Tests\n720: \n721: 1. **向后兼容性**\n722:    - 验证现有构建脚本仍可工作\n723:    - 验证 CI/CD 配置无需修改\n724: \n725: 2. **破坏性变更检测**\n726:    - 监控构建行为变化\n727:    - 验证产物一致性\n728: \n729: ## API Specification\n730: \n731: ### Makefile 目标\n732: \n733: ```makefile\n734: # 构建目标\n735: .PHONY: build build-go build-python\n736: build: build-go build-python    # 构建所有产物\n737: build-go:                       # 构建 Go 二进制文件\n738: build-python:                   # 构建 Python 包\n739: \n740: # 测试目标\n741: .PHONY: test test-go test-python test-integration\n742: test: test-go test-python       # 运行所有测试\n743: test-go:                        # 运行 Go 测试\n744: test-python:                    # 运行 Python 测试\n745: test-integration:               # 运行集成测试\n746: \n747: # Lint 目标\n748: .PHONY: lint lint-go lint-python format\n749: lint: lint-go lint-python       # 运行所有 lint 检查\n750: lint-go:                        # 运行 Go lint\n751: lint-python:                    # 运行 Python lint\n752: format:                         # 格式化所有代码\n753: \n754: # Docker 目标\n755: .PHONY: docker-build docker-push\n756: docker-build:                   # 构建 Docker 镜像\n757: docker-push:                    # 推送镜像\n758: \n759: # 清理目标\n760: .PHONY: clean clean-all\n761: clean:                          # 清理构建产物\n762: clean-all:                      # 清理所有产物和缓存\n763: \n764: # 帮助目标\n765: .PHONY: help\n766: help:                           # 显示帮助信息\n767: ```\n768: \n769: ### 变量\n770: \n771: ```makefile\n772: # Go 相关\n773: GO := go\n774: GO_VERSION := 1.24\n775: GOFLAGS :=\n776: BUILD_DIR := bin\n777: GO_BUILD_FLAGS := -ldflags=\"-s -w\"\n778: \n779: # Python 相关\n780: PYTHON := python3\n781: PIP := pip3\n782: PYTHON_VERSION := 3.11\n783: \n784: # Docker 相关\n785: DOCKER := docker\n786: DOCKER_REGISTRY :=\n787: IMAGE_NAME := agentcube\n788: IMAGE_TAG := latest\n789: \n790: # 构建相关\n791: BUILD_MODE := dev\n792: BUILD_TIME := $(shell date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)\n793: GIT_COMMIT := $(shell git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo \"unknown\")\n794: \n795: # 测试相关\n796: TEST_FLAGS :=\n797: TEST_COVERAGE := coverage.out\n798: ```\n799: \n800: ### 使用示例\n801: \n802: ```bash\n803: # 显示帮助\n804: make help\n805: \n806: # 构建所有\n807: make build\n808: \n809: # 构建特定组件\n810: make build-agentd\n811: make build-picod\n812: \n813: # 运行测试\n814: make test\n815: \n816: # 运行特定测试\n817: make test-go\n818: make test-python\n819: \n820: # Lint 检查\n821: make lint\n822: \n823: # 格式化代码\n824: make format\n825: \n826: # 清理\n827: make clean\n828: \n829: # Docker 构建\n830: make docker-build\n831: \n832: # 并行构建\n833: make -j build\n834: \n835: # 使用特定 Go 版本构建\n836: GO_VERSION=1.23 make build\n837: \n838: # 发布模式构建\n839: BUILD_MODE=release make build\n840: ```\n841: \n842: ## Configuration\n843: \n844: ### 必需工具\n845: \n846: | 工具 | 最低版本 | 用途 |\n847: |------|---------|------|\n848: | GNU Make | 4.0 | 构建系统 |\n849: | Go | 1.24 | Go 语言 |\n850: | Python | 3.11 | Python 运行时 |\n851: | Docker | 20.10 | 容器构建 |\n852: | Git | 2.0 | 版本控制 |\n853: \n854: ### 可选工具\n855: \n856: | 工具 | 最低版本 | 用途 |\n857: |------|---------|------|\n858: | golangci-lint | 1.50 | Go lint |\n859: | ruff | 0.1 | Python lint |\n860: | black | 23.0 | Python 格式化 |\n861: | goimports | latest | Go import 格式化 |\n862: | hadolint | 2.10 | Dockerfile lint |\n863: | trivy | 0.40 | 容器安全扫描 |\n864: \n865: ### 环境变量\n866: \n867: | 变量 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n868: |------|--------|------|\n869: | `GO_VERSION` | `1.24` | Go 版本 |\n870: | `BUILD_MODE` | `dev` | 构建模式（dev/release/test） |\n871: | `BUILD_DIR` | `bin` | 构建产物目录 |\n872: | `DOCKER_REGISTRY` | `` | Docker 仓库地址 |\n873: | `IMAGE_NAME` | `agentcube` | Docker 镜像名称 |\n874: | `IMAGE_TAG` | `latest` | Docker 镜像标签 |\n875: | `VERBOSE` | `0` | 详细输出（0/1） |\n876: \n877: ### 配置文件\n878: \n879: ```makefile\n880: # .makefile.env (可选，本地配置)\n881: GO_VERSION := 1.23\n882: DOCKER_REGISTRY := docker.io/myorg\n883: ```\n884: \n885: ## Security Considerations\n886: \n887: 1. **依赖安全**\n888:    - 验证 Go 依赖哈希（`go mod verify`）\n889:    - 使用固定版本依赖\n890:    - 定期更新依赖\n891: \n892: 2. **构建安全**\n893:    - 不在镜像中包含敏感信息\n894:    - 使用 `.dockerignore` 排除敏感文件\n895:    - 验证产物签名（如果需要）\n896: \n897: 3. **运行时安全**\n898:    - 非 root 用户运行容器\n899:    - 最小化容器权限\n900:    - 安全扫描镜像\n901: \n902: 4. **密钥管理**\n903:    - 不在 Makefile 中硬编码密钥\n904:    - 使用环境变量传递敏感信息\n905:    - 使用密钥管理系统\n906: \n907: ## Performance Considerations\n908: \n909: 1. **构建时间优化**\n910:    - 充分利用 Make 增量构建\n911:    - 并行构建支持（`make -j`）\n912:    - 依赖缓存\n913: \n914: 2. **并行构建策略**\n915:    - Go 和 Python 构建可以并行\n916:    - 测试可以并行（`make -j test`）\n917:    - Docker 构建独立执行\n918: \n919: 3. **缓存利用**\n920:    - Go mod 缓存\n921:    - Python pip 缓存\n922:    - Docker 层缓存\n923: \n924: 4. **内存使用**\n925:    - 限制并行构建数量\n926:    - 使用 `--max-old-space-size` 限制 Node 内存\n927:    - 监控构建资源使用\n928: \n929: ## Monitoring and Metrics\n930: \n931: ### 构建指标\n932: \n933: - 构建时间（总时间、各阶段时间）\n934: - 增量构建命中率\n935: - 并行构建效率\n936: - 失败率\n937: \n938: ### 产物指标\n939: \n940: - 二进制文件大小\n941: - Docker 镜像大小\n942: - 测试覆盖率\n943: - Lint 错误数\n944: \n945: ### 日志\n946: \n947: ```makefile\n948: # 启用详细日志\n949: VERBOSE=1 make build\n950: \n951: # 构建日志\n952: build.log: build\n953: \t@make build > build.log 2>&1\n954: \n955: # 彩色输出\n956: BLUE := \\033[0;34m\n957: GREEN := \\033[0;32m\n958: YELLOW := \\033[1;33m\n959: NC := \\033[0m\n960: ```\n961: \n962: ## Success Criteria\n963: \n964: - 所有目标正常工作\n965: - 构建时间与现有流程相当或更优\n966: - 增量构建显著加速\n967: - 并行构建正确且高效\n968: - 帮助信息清晰完整\n969: - 所有测试通过\n970: - 覆盖率达到 80%+\n971: - 文档完整准确\n972: - 开发者满意度高\n973: - CI/CD 集成成功\n974: \n975: ## Open Questions\n976: \n977: 1. **Q1**: 是否需要支持 Windows 构建？\n978:    - **当前**: 仅支持 Linux 和 macOS\n979:    - **讨论**: Windows 开发者需求\n980:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n981: \n982: 2. **Q2**: 是否需要集成缓存服务（如 BuildKit）？\n983:    - **当前**: 使用本地缓存\n984:    - **讨论**: 分布式缓存可加速 CI/CD\n985:    - **决策**: 考虑在 CI/CD AR 中添加\n986: \n987: 3. **Q3**: 是否需要支持自定义构建脚本？\n988:    - **当前**: 所有逻辑在 Makefile 中\n989:    - **讨论**: 复杂逻辑可能需要脚本\n990:    - **决策**: 使用 `scripts/` 目录处理复杂逻辑\n991: \n992: 4. **Q4**: 是否需要支持目标别名？\n993:    - **当前**: 无别名\n994:    - **讨论**: 简化常见操作\n995:    - **决策**: 添加常用别名（如 `b` → `build`）\n996: \n997: ## Next Steps\n998: \n999: 1. 实现 Phase 1-2（基础结构和 Go 目标）\n1000: 2. 实现 Phase 3-4（Python 和 Docker 目标）\n1001: 3. 实现 Phase 5-6（测试、Lint 和清理目标）\n1002: 4. 实现 Phase 7-8（开发工具和文档目标）\n1003: 5. 实现 Phase 9-10（集成测试和文档）\n1004: 6. 集成到 CI/CD 流程\n1005: 7. 收集用户反馈\n1006: 8. 持续优化和改进\n1007: \n1008: ## References\n1009: \n1010: - [GNU Make Manual](https://www.gnu.org/software/make/manual/)\n1011: - [Effective Makefile](https://clarkgrubb.com/makefile-style-guide)\n1012: - [Go Build System](https://golang.org/doc/install/source)\n1013: - [Python Packaging](https://packaging.python.org/)\n1014: - [Docker Build](https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/)\n1015: - [Kubernetes Makefile](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/Makefile)\n1016: - [Docker Makefile](https://github.com/docker/docker-ce/blob/master/components/packaging/Makefile)\n1017: - [AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建](../AR-032/proposal.md)\n1018: - [AgentCube Project](../../README.md)\n\n(End of file - total 1018 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n## Overview\n\n为 AgentCube 项目在根目录创建统一的 Makefile 构建目标体系，提供标准化的构建、测试、清理、代码质量检查和容器镜像构建操作。该 Makefile 将整合 Go 二进制文件构建、Python 包管理、多语言测试、Docker 镜像构建以及开发工作流自动化，为开发者提供单一入口点来执行所有常见任务。\n\n## Purpose\n\n实现统一的 Makefile 构建目标体系，达到以下目标：\n\n- **统一构建接口** - 提供单一入口点执行所有构建、测试、清理操作\n- **多语言支持** - 同时支持 Go 和 Python 项目的构建和测试\n- **开发效率提升** - 通过标准化的目标和别名简化常见操作\n- **CI/CD 友好** - 目标命名和输出格式便于 CI/CD 管道集成\n- **可扩展性** - 模块化设计便于添加新的构建目标和规则\n- **一致性** - 确保所有团队成员使用相同的构建命令和参数\n- **自文档化** - 通过 help 目标提供完整的使用说明\n\n## Module\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775888086348,"end":1775888086378}}}}
