{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775888131200,"sessionID":"ses_284d26f6cffep1c53tLhzWJxzP","part":{"id":"prt_d7b2e6468001wgVdh5fYiMhDyi","messageID":"msg_d7b2e2ba000188UdLMKYKK6fzn","sessionID":"ses_284d26f6cffep1c53tLhzWJxzP","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-c35b208f1d514ca2acb48a503cca1798","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-036 — Dify 插件集成 Tasks\n\n**Module**: `integrations`\n**Language**: Python\n**Size**: M\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Dify API client implementation\n- [ ] Review Dify API documentation\n- [ ] Design Dify client interface\n- [ ] Implement Dify API client class\n- [ ] Add authentication support\n- [ ] Add error handling\n- [ ] Add request/response logging\n\n**Verification**: Dify client can successfully authenticate and make API calls\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: Plugin registration mechanism\n- [ ] Design plugin registration interface\n- [ ] Implement plugin discovery\n- [ ] Implement plugin lifecycle management\n- [ ] Add plugin configuration validation\n- [ ] Add plugin health checks\n\n**Verification**: Plugins can be registered, discovered, and managed properly\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Configuration management\n- [ ] Define Dify configuration schema\n- [ ] Implement configuration loading\n- [ ] Add environment variable support\n- [ ] Add configuration validation\n- [ ] Add configuration hot-reload support\n\n**Verification**: Configuration can be loaded and validated correctly\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Error handling and retry logic\n- [ ] Implement error classification\n- [ ] Add retry mechanism for transient errors\n- [ ] Add circuit breaker pattern\n- [ ] Add timeout handling\n- [ ] Add error logging and metrics\n\n**Verification**: Errors are handled gracefully with appropriate retry logic\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: Unit tests\n- [ ] Write Dify client unit tests\n- [ ] Write plugin registration tests\n- [ ] Write configuration management tests\n- [ ] Write error handling tests\n- [ ] Achieve 80%+ code coverage\n\n**Verification**: All unit tests pass with high coverage\n\n---\n\n### Task 6: Integration tests\n- [ ] Write Dify API integration tests\n- [ ] Write end-to-end plugin tests\n- [ ] Test error scenarios\n- [ ] Test configuration scenarios\n\n**Verification**: All integration tests pass\n\n---\n\n### Task 7: Documentation\n- [ ] Write Dify integration documentation\n- [ ] Write plugin development guide\n- [ ] Write configuration reference\n- [ ] Add code examples\n\n**Verification**: Documentation is complete and accurate\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**Total Tasks**: 7\n**Estimated Effort**: M (Medium) - 15-20 hours\n\n### Key Deliverables\n1. **Dify API client** with authentication and error handling\n2. **Plugin registration mechanism** for Dify integration\n3. **Configuration management** for Dify settings\n4. **Comprehensive tests** (unit and integration)\n5. **Complete documentation** for users and developers\n\n### Success Criteria\n- Dify client can authenticate and make API calls successfully\n- Plugins can be registered and discovered properly\n- Configuration can be loaded and validated correctly\n- Error handling works with appropriate retry logic\n- All tests pass with 80%+ coverage\n- Documentation is complete and accurate\n\n### Dependencies\n- Python 3.10+\n- Dify API access and credentials\n- Existing integrations module structure\n\n### Blocked By\n- None\n\n### Blocks\n- None currently identified\n\n### Notes\n- Dify integration should be optional and configurable\n- Follow existing plugin patterns in the integrations module\n- Ensure proper error handling for production use\n- Add comprehensive logging for debugging","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-036/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-036/tasks.md","exists":false